    <h1>Accounts receivable</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>CRM » AR list</strong> menu provides you with an overview of all outstanding receivables. All contacts with outstanding claims are listed.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="preparatory-settings">1. Preparatory settings</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can set default settings for <a href="/en/crm/ar-list#search">search filters</a> of the AR list in the <strong>Setup » CRM » Settings</strong> menu. Pay attention to the explanations given in <a href="#table-default-settings-filters-ar-list">Table 1</a>.</p>
</div>
<table id="table-default-settings-filters-ar-list" class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
