<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-default-filter-contact-type">Filter contact type</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Decide which <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts#20">contact types</a> should be available for the corresponding filter in the AR list. If you don’t select anything for this setting, the contact types guest and customer are available for this filter.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-default-filter-customer-class">Filter Customer class</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Decide which <strong>customer classes</strong> should be available for the corresponding filter in the AR list. If you don’t select a customer class in this setting, all <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts#15">customer classes</a> are available for the corresponding filter in the AR list.</p></td>
