<div class="paragraph">
<p>To make the AR list visible for users with <strong>Back end</strong> access, select the option. Open the user account in the <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Rights » User</strong> menu and select in the <strong>Menu visibilities</strong> area the option <strong>CRM &gt; AR list</strong>.</p>
</div>
</td>
