This is a default column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-type">Type</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The contact type of the contact with open claims is displayed.<br>
This is a default column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-first-name">First name</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The first name of the contact with open claims is displayed.<br>
This is a default column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-last-name">Last name</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The last name of the contact with open claims is displayed.<br>
This is a default column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-email">Email</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The email address of the contact with open claims is displayed.<br>
This is a default column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong id="intable-ar-list-company">Company</strong></p></td>
